title: [SOLVED]Macbook air 820-00165 Dead no greenlight no PPBUS_G3H
message:
Hi guys, I have a 820-00165 without PPBUS_G3H.

I don’t know where start to fix. Seems like a short to ground but Im not sure.

I let you see my measures. 


PPBUS_G3H :  0.50v @ F7140 (Its pretty curious but that measure is going down so slowly)
PPDCIN_G3H_ISOL: 14.93v @ R7005 Pin 1

PP3V42_G3H: @ C5120 2.52v

On U7100

Pin 19 & 20 : 5.05v

Pin 2 : 14.71v

Resistance between pins 17 - 18 : 3.3 Ohms

Resistance betweens pins 27 - 28 : 20.0 Ohms

Pin 27 - 28 : 14.5 v

Helpme!

title: [SOLVED]Macbook air 820-00165 Dead no greenlight no PPBUS_G3H
message: 2.7V on L7095 is too low, check if feedback resistors are ok (R7095-R7096), other than that , U7090 is bad....
